{"id":268915,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2012/12/维权网-上海50名民众旁听被拒，周雪珍劳教案听证/","date":"2012-12-18T13:45:36Z","modified":"2012-12-18T13:45:36Z","title":"维权网 | 上海50名民众旁听被拒，周雪珍劳教案听证会无端取消（组图）","content":"<p><div dir=\"ltr\"></p>\n<div></div>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" name='more'></a></p>\n<div><span>（维权网信息员孙小芸报道）</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">12</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">17</span><span>日下午</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2</span><span>时</span><span>，是上海市第二中级法院书面通知周雪珍召开关于劳教一案的听证会的时间。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>周雪珍在今年人权日（</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">12</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">10</span><span>日</span><span>星期一）下午约</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">5</span><span>时，接到一个自称是上海市第二中级法院书记员 姚 君君的电话说：“你这个星期三开劳教听证会”。周雪珍表明自己在老家江苏启东来不及赶回上海。 姚 君君说：“放在下个星期吧，短信通知你”。周雪珍明确告知对方：“对不起，短信我搞不来（‘搞不来’的意思是：不会使用短信），最好给我一个书面通知书吧”。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>本月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">12</span><span>日上午</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">8</span><span>时，周雪珍果然收到了一个关于劳教听证会的书面通知书。于是周雪珍按照通知书上的时间、地点提前赴约等候。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">50</span><span>多位上海维权人士得知周雪珍开劳教听证会的消息后，也提前半小时赶到二中院等候，要求旁听，却被二中院拒绝。维权人士们等到下午</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">4</span><span>时，二中院仍不给周雪珍开听证会，周雪珍要求二中院作出书面解释，二中院无言以对。后来以“下班了”为由将周雪珍和维权人士们一起赶出法院大门。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"> </span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>周雪珍因交通事故成了残疾人，又因房屋被强拆，丈夫被害死而依法维权，却遭到拘留、劳教。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">2010</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">12</span><span>月，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">55</span><span>周岁（已经到了退休年龄）超过</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">5</span><span>个月的周雪珍被上海市劳动教养管理委员会作出（</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2010</span><span>）沪劳委审字第</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">4405</span><span>号《上海市劳动教养管理委员会劳动教养决定书》，对其收容劳动教养</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">1</span><span>年零</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">3</span><span>个月。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>周雪珍叹声叹气地表示：本来自己该安享晚年，却因合法的财产被抢，丈夫屈死，上访被拘留被劳教，独裁专制官官相护，老百姓控诉无门。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>周雪珍请求媒体和各界正义人士继续关注她被劳教一案的申诉。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span><br /></span></div>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-U8fShlymKes/UNBEJym1SuI/AAAAAAAAW-0/AnIC8WkREfs/s1600/P1000188.JPG\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"223\" src=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-U8fShlymKes/UNBEJym1SuI/AAAAAAAAW-0/AnIC8WkREfs/s320/P1000188.JPG\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<table align=\"center\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-8l3I1hVgnOM/UNBEMcNcW8I/AAAAAAAAW-8/spL2boDqmcc/s1600/P1000189.JPG\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"204\" src=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-8l3I1hVgnOM/UNBEMcNcW8I/AAAAAAAAW-8/spL2boDqmcc/s320/P1000189.JPG\" width=\"320\" /></a></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>声援周雪珍的维权人士在第二中级法院外合影留念</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-AlHyvu38YBo/UNBENnXWZFI/AAAAAAAAW_E/C6KMRZLVN1U/s1600/P1000191.JPG\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"197\" src=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-AlHyvu38YBo/UNBENnXWZFI/AAAAAAAAW_E/C6KMRZLVN1U/s320/P1000191.JPG\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-z_EVISTLY34/UNBEQE0qOaI/AAAAAAAAW_M/lnZHrD7_Z90/s1600/DSCI0475.JPG\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"240\" src=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-z_EVISTLY34/UNBEQE0qOaI/AAAAAAAAW_M/lnZHrD7_Z90/s320/DSCI0475.JPG\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-erV_WraJwlI/UNBETD9r0-I/AAAAAAAAW_U/f6RNoWsnHFU/s1600/DSCI0482.JPG\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"240\" src=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-erV_WraJwlI/UNBETD9r0-I/AAAAAAAAW_U/f6RNoWsnHFU/s320/DSCI0482.JPG\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-IeZNb0h-bJw/UN